Synopsis:
   $ovserver(<index>)

Technical:
   This function associates a server' short name with the given index number.

Practical:
   This function is used to convert from a server's index number to its
   short name.  This short name is traditionally used by OperView.

Returns:
   short name of server, if any

See Also:
   server(1); servnum(6); servname(6); winserv(6)

